Set Field-Level Security to Analytics Integration User

Before creating the Analytics for Communications - Order Tracking app, ensure the Analytics Cloud Integration User profile has access to all used fields.

Available in: Developer, Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions where B2B Communications Cloud is enabled

From Setup, enter the object name, select Fields & Relationships, then the field to edit. Select Set Field-Level Security for the Analytics Cloud Integration User profile and save changes. Repeat this process for all used fields on all objects.

Repeat these steps for all of the fields on all of the objects that the app uses.
title: Setting Field-Level Security for Analytics Integration User
